      "provider": "copilot",
      "providerName": "Microsoft Copilot",
      "providerColor": "#0078D4",
      "date": "2026-03-14",
      "text": "What changed: Copilot now provides inline citations for connector-based results, with a hover experience that displays a glance card summarizing the cited entity, and a deep citation view available when users select the citation for more detail.",
