      "providerName": "Microsoft Copilot",
      "providerColor": "#0078D4",
      "date": "2026-03-14",
      "text": "Why: Users want clearer insight into how Copilot-generated results are created, especially when responses are based on external or connected data sources. This update improves transparency by explaining the origin of information through richer citation details.",
